-search artists in spotify
-display results in a table
-user selects an artist, then their albums will appear in the table
-user selects an album, then the tracks from that album will appear
-user selects a song, it will play and display the lyrics (called from a song lyrics API)
-allow the user to search for other songs while current song is playing
-separate html elements for each relevant piece of data
	-panel that fills in with rows for each search result
	-once a result is clicked another panel fills with that artist's albums
	-once an album is clicked another panel fills with that album's tracks
	-user can select a track and have it play
		-display lyrics, progress bar, album cover, song name, album, and artist below the panels that hold the search results